# Meet Scheduling

Meet Scheduling is a backend application that helps users create and manage meetings. 
The main purpose of this project is to provide APIs for scheduling meetings and managing meeting details.

## Technologies Used

- Java
- Spring Boot
- Spring Data JPA
- Hibernate
- MySQL
- REST API

## Features

- User can create meetings
- Manage meeting details
- Update and delete meetings
- Store meeting information in database
- RESTful APIs for handling requests

## Project Structure

The project follows layered architecture:

Controller Layer - Handles API requests  
Service Layer - Contains business logic  
Repository Layer - Database operations  

## How To Run

1. Clone the repository
2. Configure database details
3. Run the Spring Boot application

